translations: n.椭圆形物；卵形体（oval 的复数）

sentences.sentence: As you can see, two of the ovals have no labels.
sentences.translation: 正如您看到的，有两个椭圆形框中没有任何标签。

sentences.sentence: Buy only the ovals — the round ones tend to have more seeds and less "meat."
sentences.translation: 椭圆形的为上选，因为圆形肚脐的往往有较多的籽而肉却不多。
